title: COMODO Internet Security 8.0.0.4314 Beta 2
description:
Hello Everyone,

We are excited to announce that COMODO Internet Security 8.0.0.4314 Beta 2 is ready for your review.

Thank you very much for your cooperation and support during the BETA testing! Thanks to your feedback and the excellent work of our teams worldwide, we have addressed 50+ bugs and several improvements over the last CIS 8.0 Beta release. You can see a selected set of these in release notes section below.

What's new in 8.0.0.4314?

New

New UI Theme

    "Flat Tile" theme with updated icons and colors for better look and feel.

Viruscope Recognizers grid in ASE

    List of registered recognizers
    Possibility to manage each recognizer state, turn it ON and OFF


Fixed

We have addressed 50+ issues reported by our users in this release
